How many patients are younger than 40?

```{r}
sum(age < 40)

```

How many patients are older than 25, and have an FEV1 between 40 and 70 (inclusive)?
```{r}
age_logical <- age > 25

fev1_logical <- (fev1 >= 40) & (fev1 <= 70)

sum(age_logical & fev1_logical)
```
